Instructions for using the DrawingApp

Save: draw you graph, then enter the desired name in the box. The graph will be saved as .graph and .png in your folder.
Open: enter the path to the folder that contains your .graph files. All graphs from the folder will be loaded and the stairs and elevator
will be connected.
Export: after opening your graphs, save your final graph by entering the desired name in the box. Press "Reset" and then "Export" and 
choose the .graph file corresponding to your final graph. A .json file with the same name will be created.
